{"tid":1969004,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"僱主有無信心妙計擊敗IQ180(自稱)羅致光？ 若企業圖以「妙計」獲利　或改薪酬計算選項","createTime":"2020-04-12T06:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T06:26:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3546092ace174e94bc7cabc8cd520758838cc19e","tid":1969004,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T06:26:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1520112_1_L_20200411125630.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1520112_1_L_20200411125630.jpg&h=6c5a75f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府推出800億元的保就業計劃，勞工及福利局局長羅致光承認，難以逐一調查申請保就業資助的僱主，所支付的薪酬是否合理，認為只要不涉及欺騙，無傷大雅的情況可以接受。<br />\n<br />\n但羅致光表示，若企業有妙計，想利用計劃從中獲利，不排除更改薪酬計算基礎的選項，當局會抽查有不正常減薪的個案，並有權收回部分資助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1520112-20200411.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1520112-20200411.htm&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zoj3WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=331f80f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1520112-20200411.htm&h=c6bfb515\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1520112-20200411.htm</a>"}]}